#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure <guilabel>FTP Options</guilabel> here. At present there is "
"just two options:"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko skonfigurirate <guilabel>FTP Možnosti</guilabel>. Trenutno sta "
"tukaj le dve možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable passive mode (PASV)"
msgstr "Omogoči pasivni način (PASV)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Passive &FTP; is often required when you are behind a firewall. Many "
"firewalls only permit connections that were initiated from <quote>the "
"inside</quote>. Passive &FTP; is controlled by the client, which makes it "
"usable through firewalls."
msgstr ""
"Pasivni &FTP; je pogosto potreben, ko se vaš računalnik nahaja za požarnim "
"zidom. Veliko požarnih zidov dovoljuje le povezave, ki so bile vzpostavljene "
"<quote>od znotraj</quote>. Pasivni &FTP; nadzoruje odjemalec, zato se ga "
"lahko uporablja skozi požarne zidove."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mark partially uploaded files"
msgstr "Označi delno naložene datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a mark is placed in this box, partially uploaded files will have a "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.part</literal> extension added to the end of "
"the file. This extension is removed once the file download is complete."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to polje označeno, bodo imele delno naložene datoteke <literal role="
"\"extension\">.part</literal> pripono na koncu datoteke. Ta pripona je "
"odstranjena, ko je datoteka do konca naložena."

#~ msgid "timeouts"
#~ msgstr "časovne omejitve"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Here you can set timeout values. You might want to tweak them if your "
#~ "connection is very slow, but the default settings are appropriate for "
#~ "most users."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Tukaj lahko nastavite dolžine intervalov časovnih omejitev. Če je vaša "
#~ "povezava počasna, jih lahko prilagodite, sicer pa so privzete nastavitve "
#~ "primerne za večino uporabnikov."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Here <guilabel>Timeout Values</guilabel> are the length of time an "
#~ "application should wait for an answer from a network operation."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Tukaj <guilabel>Vrednosti Časovnih Omejitev</guilabel> pomenijo, koliko "
#~ "časa naj aplikacija čaka na odgovor iz strani omrežja."

#~ msgid "You can configure the following timeouts:"
#~ msgstr "Lahko konfigurirate nasledje časovne omejitve:"

#~ msgid "Socket read:"
#~ msgstr "Branje vtiča:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Some applications use <firstterm>sockets</firstterm> to communicate. You "
#~ "can think of a socket as a water tap; while it is open, water (or in our "
#~ "case, data) comes out, without any interaction. If something stops this "
#~ "flow of data, the application will wait for more to come. This could be a "
#~ "very long time, but you can configure a maximum time for an application "
#~ "to wait with this option."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Nekatere aplikacije uporabljajo <firstterm>vtiče</firstterm> za "
#~ "komunikacijo. Vtiče si lahko predstavljate kot vodne pipe; dokler so "
#~ "odprte, voda (ali v našem primeru podatki) priteče brez interakcij. Če "
#~ "nekaj prekine ta tok podatkov, bo aplikacija počakala, da pridejo "
#~ "naslednji. To lahko traja zelo veliko časa, zato lahko nastavite "
#~ "maksimalen čas, preden aplikacija preneha čakati na podatke."

#~ msgid "This setting will only apply to &kde; applications, of course."
#~ msgstr "Ta nastavitev se bo seveda uveljavila le pri &kde; aplikacijah."

#~ msgid "Proxy connect:"
#~ msgstr "Povezava do posrednika:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Sets how long to wait for a connection to a proxy server, if one is "
#~ "configured."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Nastavi čas čakanja na povezavo s proxy strežnikom, če je ta "
#~ "skonfiguriran."

#~ msgid "Server connect:"
#~ msgstr "Povezava s strežnikom:"

#~ msgid "Sets how long to wait for a connection to a remote server."
#~ msgstr "Nastavi čas čakanja na povezavo z oddaljenim strežnikom."

#~ msgid "Server response:"
#~ msgstr "Odgovor strežnika:"

#~ msgid "Sets how long to wait for a reply from a remote server."
#~ msgstr "Nastavi čas čakanja na odgovor oddaljenega strežnika."

#~ msgid "Not yet documented"
#~ msgstr "Dokumentacija ĹĄe ni na voljo."
